h%C3%A1t/poem-QTVFJ9Z0-BPrKIIARvfJrA">Tảo phát - 早發</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%C3%B4/Ti%E1%BB%83u-chu/poem-U5ro2DHTHCi6DAS2FwvxLA">Tiểu chu - 小舟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%C3%B4/author-LbaVSB66mX6k1U09t5TO2A">Lâm Bô</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Cao/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-L%C3%B4-chu-trung-d%E1%BA%A1-to%E1%BA%A1/poem-XMclnL5Rr1lxquF5JLF1JA">Trường Lô chu trung dạ toạ - 長蘆舟中夜坐</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Cao/author-MTb08tvONGpKu1ngOWpQ5Q">Doãn Đình Cao</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Th%E1%BB%A5-Ho%C3%A0i-Th%C3%A2m/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-tWMM7Zo-ObPcD6qLyYSggw">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Th%E1%BB%A5-Ho%C3%A0i-Th%C3%A2m/author-S1-olF1e8UdkYRJzaPYUOw">Từ Thụ Hoài Thâm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
